name: Ulectric
0:
”Alexa open u lectric”
”Alexa ask u lectric find charger”
”Alexa ask u lectric find nearest charger”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: u. lectric
Developer Terms of Use
des:
U lectric help to find nearest EV charging station. If you use this skill from you phone, tablet any device that support geo location services, U lectric will automatically find nearest EV chargers, also U lectric can show you the detail route to EV station with help of navigation. 
You can also use custom search to specify:
- level of charging station (level 1, level 2, fast),
- connector types (AC, Chademo ...) 
- city (New York, Wahington ...)
- or operator of EV charging station (Tesla, EV Connect ...)
you are looking for.
